ntly only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/group\"><code>group()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupCollapsed\"><code>groupCollapsed()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupEnd\"><code>groupEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/info\"><code>info()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Console/log\"><code>log()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profile\"><code>profile()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profileEnd\"><code>profileEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/table\"><code>table()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/time\"><code>time()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeEnd\"><code>timeEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeLog\"><code>timeLog()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/trace\"><code>trace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/warn\"><code>warn()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Console API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/console\"><code>Window.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Niestandardowy:</strong> This feature is non-standard and is not on a standards track. Do not use it on production sites facing the Web: it will not work for every user. There may also be large incompatibilities between implementations and the behavior may change in the future.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Wyświetla tekst w konsoli.</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Workers (en-US)</a></p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">console.log(<em>obj1</em> [, <em>obj2</em>, ..., <em>objN</em>]);\nconsole.log(<em>msg</em> [, <em>subst1</em>, ..., <em>substN</em>]);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"obj1\"><code>obj1</code> ... <code>objN</code></dt>\n <dd>Lista obiektów JavaScript do wyświelenia. Podane obiekty są kolejno dołączane i przekazywane na wyjście.</dd>\n <dt id=\"msg\"><code>msg</code></dt>\n <dd>String JavaScript zawierający zero lub więcej stringów podmieniających.</dd>\n <dt id=\"subst1\"><code>subst1</code> ... <code>substN</code></dt>\n <dd>Obiekt JavaScript w którym zastępowane są stringi podmieniające z msg. &nbsp;Daje Ci to dodatkową kontrolę nad formatem.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>Zobacz również&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console#outputting_text_to_the_console\">Outputting text to the console</a> w dokumentacji <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>console</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specyfikacja</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komentarz</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://console.spec.whatwg.org/#consolelogobject--object-\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Console API<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'console.log()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Początkowa definicja</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.Console.log","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_również","title":"Zobacz również","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.opera.com/dragonfly/documentation/console/\" rel=\" noopener\">Opera Dragonfly documentation: Console</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/gg589530\" rel=\" noopener\">MSDN: Using the F12 Tools Console to View Errors and Status</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://getfirebug.com/wiki/index.php/Console_API\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Firebug wiki: Console API</a> - Firebug supports additional features in its console.log() implementation, such as <a href=\"http://www.softwareishard.com/blog/firebug/firebug-tip-styled-logging/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">styled logging</a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/console.html#console_console_log_data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">NodeJS: Console API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Parameters","id":"parameters"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Zobacz również","id":"zobacz_również"}],"summary":"Wyświetla tekst w konsoli.","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"console.log","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"fold